<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4471875>
    dc:description "FIGURE 34. Zagrammosoma multilineatum, ♀: (A) head, frontolateral, (B) lateral habitus, (C) fore wing, dorsal, (D) dorsal habitus; (E) ♁ dorsal habitus. Scale bar = 0.2 mm (A), 0.5 mm (B–E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4471875/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4471853>
    dc:description "FIGURE 23. Zagrammosoma interlineatum stat. rev., ♀: (A) head, frontolateral, (B) lateral habitus, (C) fore wing, dorsal, (D) dorsal habitus; (E) ♁ dorsal habitus. Scale bar = 0.2 mm (A), 0.5 mm (B–E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4471853/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4471815>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Zagrammosoma americanum, ♀: (A) head, frontolateral, (B) lateral habitus-medial darkening on hind wing artifact from point mount, (C) fore wing, dorsal, (D) dorsal habitus; (E) ♁ dorsal habitus. Scale bar = 0.2 mm (A), 0.5m (B–E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4471815/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4471843>
    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Zagrammosoma galapagoense n. sp., ♀: (A) head, frontolateral, (B) lateral habitus, (C) fore wing, dorsal, (D) dorsal habitus; (E–F) ♁ dorsal habitus. Scale bar = 0.2 mm (A, E, F), 0.5 mm (B–D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4471843/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4471831>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Zagrammosoma crowei, ♀: (A) head, frontal, (B) lateral habitus, (C) fore wing, dorsal, (D) dorsal habitus; (E) ♁ dorsal habitus. Scale bar = 0.2 mm (A), 0.5 mm (B–E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4471831/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4471877>
    dc:description "FIGURE 35. Distribution of Zagrammosoma multilineatum." ;
